quran[59]{c,v,t}:
  26,52,"Ni twan’juwulile Musa (maloŵe ganti): “Ŵigulani lwachilo ni achikapolo Ŵangu, chisimu ŵanganyammwe tinkuuyidwe.”"
  26,53,Basi Firiauna ni jwatumisye m’misinda (josope) akusonganganya
  26,54,"(Ŵaŵapitaga nchigombelesya yanti): “Chisimu ŵanganyaŵa (ŵanache ŵa Israila) ali kwene kankutula kannono.”"
  26,55,“Soni chisimu ŵanganyao akutupikasya ntima.”
  26,56,“Soni chisimu uwwe tuli wosope (ŵajinji nambo soni) tuli mesope (tukwalolechesya ŵanganyao kuti akatupatisya ipato iliyose).”
  26,57,Basi Uwwe ni twakopwesye ŵanganyao (ŵanya Afiriauna) m’matimbe ni achitutumule
  26,58,Kwisa soni mu imatiilo yachipanje ni m’malo mwakuchimbichika
  26,59,"Mwele (ni mutwatendele), ni twaitesile kuŵa yawinjilwa ni ŵanache ŵa Israila"
  26,60,Basi ŵanganyao ni ŵakuyiye (ŵanache ŵa Israilao) pakopoka kwa lyuŵa
  26,61,"Basi ndema jagaonegene makuga ganagaŵili (likuga lya Firiauna ni lya Musa), ŵandu ŵa Musa ŵatite: “Chisimu uwwe chitukamulwe.”"
  26,62,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ngwamba! Chisimu Ambuje ŵangu ali none, chanjongolele (yakutenda kuti mpaka tujokoche).”"
  26,63,"Basi ni twan’juwulile Musa (maloŵe ganti): “Putani mbwani ni simbo jenujo.” Ni jagaŵanyiche, upande uliose waliji nti chisawu litumbi lyekulungwa"
  26,64,Ni twaŵandichisye palakwepo ŵaneo (Firiauna ni ŵandu ŵakwe)
  26,65,Ni twan’jokwele Musa ni ŵaŵaliji najo imo wosopeŵene
  26,66,Kaneka ni twamisisye ŵaneo (Firiauna ni ŵandu ŵakwe)
  26,67,Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chimanyisyo (cha ukombosi wa Allah). Nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila
  26,68,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu niŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,69,Soni mwasoomelani ŵanganyao abali ja Ibrahima
  26,70,"Pandema jajwawusisye babagwe ni ŵandu ŵakwe kuti: “Chichi nkuchigalagatila?”"
  26,71,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Tukugalagatila isanamu, basi ni tukwendelechela kuigalagatila ndema ni katema.”"
  26,72,"(Ibrahima) jwatite: “Ana akasampikanaga pati nchaŵilangaga?”"
  26,73,“Kapena akasampaga chikamuchisyo (pati nchagalagatilaga) kapena kupeleka masausyo (naga ngaagalagatila)?”
  26,74,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “(Ngwamba,) Nambo twasimene achatati ŵetu achitendaga mwatukutendelamu.”"
  26,75,"(Ibrahima) jwatite: “Ana nkwaona aŵa ŵam’bele n’di nkwagalagatila,”"
  26,76,“Jenumanja ni achatati ŵenu ŵaŵalongolele?”
  26,77,"“Basi chisimu ŵanganyao ni amagongo ŵangu, ikaŵeje M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,78,"“Ajula juŵangumbile, nambo soni Jwalakwe ni jwaakunjongolela (kwitala lyagoloka).”"
  26,79,“Nambo soni Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwaakundisyaga ni kumwesya.”
  26,80,“Soni pati nwasile basi Jwalakwe ni jwaakumbosyaga.”
  26,81,"“Nambo soni Ajula jwatambe chiwa, nikwisa kumba umi soni (ku Kiyama).”"
  26,82,“Nambo soni Ajula jwangukolela tama janti tachingululuchila ileŵi yangu Lisiku Lyamalipilo.”
  26,83,"“Ambuje ŵangu! Mumbani lunda lwakwilanyichisya (ichindu), ni musimanganye ni ŵandu ŵambone.”"
  26,84,“Soni mumbani kusaalidwa kwambone m’mikutula jamunyuma.”
  26,85,“Ni mundende kuŵa mwa akujitawala Mbepo Jachindimba.”
  26,86,"“Ni mwakululuchile atati ŵangu, chisimu ŵalakweo aŵele ŵampepe mwa akusokonechela.”"
  26,87,“Soni nkaja kunjalusya pa Lisiku lyatachijimusyidwaga ŵandu m’malembe.”
  26,88,"“Lisiku lyangakamuchisya chipanje namuno ŵanache,”"
  26,89,“Ikaŵeje jwatachiika kwa Allah ni ntima weswela.”
  26,90,Ni jichiŵandichisyidwa Mbepo kwa ŵakun’jogopa (Allah)
  26,91,Ni uchionesyedwa Moto Waukali kwa ŵapombotale
  26,92,"Ni kuchiŵechetedwa kukwao: “Ali kwapi aŵala ŵamwaliji nkwagalagatila,”"
  26,93,“Kunneka Allah? Ana mpaka akombole kunkamuchisya ŵanganyammwe kapena kulikamuchisya achimisyene?”
  26,94,Basi ni tachiponyedwa chamakuku mwalakwemo ŵanganyao ni akupombotala (ŵane)
  26,95,Kwisa soni asilikali ŵa Ibulisu wosopeŵene
  26,96,"Tachiti, aku ŵanganyao achikanganaga mwalakwemo"
  26,97,“Tukunnumbila Allah! Chisimu uwwe twaliji nkusokonechela kwakuonechela.”
  26,98,“Pandema jatwannandanyaga ŵanganyammwe ni M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”
  26,99,“Ni nganatusokonesya ikaŵeje akuleŵa.”
  26,100,“Ni nganitukola akutuombola.”
  26,101,“Namuno nsyoŵe jwapantima (jwanti ni kutukamuchisya.)”
  26,102,"“Mwanti tungakole upile wakuujila (ku duniya), basi tungajiile kuŵa mwa akukulupilila.”"
  26,103,"Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chilosyo, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila"
  26,104,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,105,Ŵandu ŵa Nuhu ŵaakaaniile achimitenga
  26,106,"Ndema jaŵasalile nnongo n’jao Nuhu kuti: “Ana ngankogopa?”"
  26,107,“Chisimu une kukwenu ni Ntenga jwakulupichika.”
  26,108,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,109,"“Soni ngangun’juga pa yalakweyi malipilo, nganigaŵatu malipilo gangu ikaŵeje kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,110,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”